  "secondary": {
    "description_full": "Experience one of the most livable areas in Beijing, a neighborhood highly rated by true Beijingers and chosen as their home.\nFrom here, it's only 10 minutes by car to the Botanical Garden, 15 minutes to the famous Fragrance Hill, and about 20 minutes to the stunning Summer Palace. Taxi fare is just 5 USD.\n\nIn just 5 minutes by bike, you can explore Shougang Park --- a creative landmark where old steel factory buildings have been transformed into cultural and artistic spaces. You will be impressed!\n\nWithin 15 minutes by bike, you'll arrive at the Beijing East Olympic Park.\n\nThe metro station is only an 8-minute walk, making the whole city easily accessible.\n\nThis neighborhood combines local authenticity, green lifestyle, and cultural charm, offering you a chance to live like a true Beijinger while staying connected to nature and the city.\n\nThis is an apartment with living room, kitchen, bathroom, two bedrooms. You will stay in main bedroom with balcony and the host stay in the other one.",
